217
00:20:21,597 --> 00:20:26,228
Labi, tātad... esam bankrotējuši.

218
00:20:27,144 --> 00:20:28,896
Nu, vismaz tas ir izdarīts. Viss
beidzies.

219
00:20:28,980 --> 00:20:30,272
ES tik ļoti cenšos.

220
00:20:30,356 --> 00:20:32,275
